The paper deals with generating academic papers using advanced language modeling techniques on a dataset of $\LaTeX{}$ source files of recent computer vision papers. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the natural language processing (NLP) sub-category of computer science, which is cs.CL. Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques such as Transformers, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely candidates.
